title: Winfield's INT of Burrow seals NFC's Pro Bowl win

sources.name: ESPN NFL
sources.title: Winfield's INT of Burrow seals NFC's Pro Bowl win
sources.description: Buccaneers safety Antoine Winfield Jr. jumped a route to intercept Bengals quarterback Joe Burrow to seal the NFC's 66-52 comeback win against the AFC in the league's third Pro Bowl flag football game Tuesday night.
